<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 06:16:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于美元坚挺、美联储不确定，外国人四月份抛售亚洲债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/foreigners-sold-asian-bonds-april-amid-firm-dollar-fed-uncertainty-2024-05-17/</link><description>由于美元走强和美联储降息的不确定性抑制了投资者的兴趣，外国投资者四月份连续第二个月成为亚洲债券的净卖家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 05:59:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/foreigners-sold-asian-bonds-april-amid-firm-dollar-fed-uncertainty-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许地方政府官员以“合理”价格购买经济适用房</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-let-local-govt-officials-buy-affordable-housing-reasonable-prices-2024-05-17/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，副总理何立峰周五在住房政策在线会议上表示，中国将允许地方政府以“合理”价格购买部分住房，以提供经济适用房。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 05:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-let-local-govt-officials-buy-affordable-housing-reasonable-prices-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>ABB收购西门子在华接线配件业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abb-buys-siemenss-wiring-business-china-2024-05-17/</link><description>瑞士工程集团 ABB 周五表示，已同意收购德国竞争对手西门子在中国的接线配件业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 05:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abb-buys-siemenss-wiring-business-china-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国国有企业将于2028年推出太空旅游飞行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-state-backed-company-launch-space-tourism-flights-by-2028-2024-05-17/</link><description>据官方媒体周五报道，中国商业航天公司中科航天宣布其“太空旅游飞行器”将于 2027 年首飞，并于 2028 年前往太空边缘。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-state-backed-company-launch-space-tourism-flights-by-2028-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园香港清算听证会延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-country-gardens-hong-kong-liquidation-hearing-2024-05-17/</link><description>香港一家法院将上周五寻求清算碧桂园请愿书的听证会推迟至 6 月 11 日，在北京努力重振遭受危机打击的房地产行业之际，这为这家陷入困境的中国开发商提供了喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-country-gardens-hong-kong-liquidation-hearing-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>普京将推动莫斯科与北京在中国东北地区的贸易增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-push-growing-moscow-beijing-trade-chinas-northeast-2024-05-17/</link><description>在与中国习近平签署新时代战略伙伴关系承诺后，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周五将强调中国东北地区俄罗斯边境附近贸易日益增长的重要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-push-growing-moscow-beijing-trade-chinas-northeast-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺购买公寓并完成停滞的住房项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-pace-over-9-years-2024-05-17/</link><description>中国周五宣布了地方政府购买“部分”公寓的计划，并承诺大力交付未完工的房屋，作为稳定受危机打击的房地产行业的新一轮措施的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 02:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-pace-over-9-years-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国降息时机的不确定性导致股市波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周五下跌，交易员思考美国近期货币政策路径，此前美联储官员表示，即使通胀显示出早期放缓迹象，利率可能需要在更长时间内保持在较高水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 02:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂开工但消费持续低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-industrial-output-rises-67-beats-expectations-2024-05-17/</link><description>尽管零售销售意外放缓且房地产行业仍拖累经济，但在外部需求改善的帮助下，中国 4 月份工厂产出超出预期，给北京带来了采取更多措施支持经济增长的压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 02:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-industrial-output-rises-67-beats-expectations-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>代理顾问格拉斯刘易斯敦促赫斯股东接受雪佛龙的收购要约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/proxy-adviser-glass-lewis-urges-hess-shareholders-accept-chevron-takeover-offer-2024-05-17/</link><description>代理顾问格拉斯·刘易斯 (Glass Lewis) 周四表示，赫斯股东应在该石油公司 5 月 28 日的特别会议上投票支持雪佛龙 530 亿美元的全股票收购要约。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/proxy-adviser-glass-lewis-urges-hess-shareholders-accept-chevron-takeover-offer-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>追踪中国在台湾上空的“灰色地带”热气球飞行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tracking-chinas-grey-zone-balloon-flights-over-taiwan-2024-05-17/</link><description>大约在台湾一月份总统大选前一个月，中国开始向台湾海峡派遣入侵者：100多个气球，其中一些飞越台湾领空或台北控制的繁忙的民航空中走廊。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tracking-chinas-grey-zone-balloon-flights-over-taiwan-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国经济放缓迹象，美元每周下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-set-weekly-drop-us-slowdown-signs-2024-05-17/</link><description>由于通胀降温和美国经济疲软的迹象提高了降息的可能性，美元兑欧元周五出现两个半月来最大单周跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:13:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-set-weekly-drop-us-slowdown-signs-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国数据转储前市场乐观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪推迟2025年智利锂正极工厂计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-byd-postpones-plans-2025-chile-lithium-cathode-plant-2024-05-16/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪公司美洲区负责人周二对路透表示，该公司推迟了 2025 年在智利生产电动汽车 (EV) 电池锂阴极的计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-byd-postpones-plans-2025-chile-lithium-cathode-plant-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，美国国防部长计划在新加坡会见中国国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-plans-meet-with-chinese-counterpart-singapore-us-official-says-2024-05-16/</link><description>一位美国官员周四表示，美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀预计将于本月晚些时候在新加坡举行的一次会议上会见中国国防部长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-plans-meet-with-chinese-counterpart-singapore-us-official-says-2024-05-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>